0 million of fines</a> for this stuff last year.=C2=A0Every bank is going t=
o fire a bunch of people and pay=C2=A0nine-digit fines over, like, =E2=80=
=9Cyou used WhatsApp to invite a client to play golf.=E2=80=9D There will b=
